title: Batman - Death and the Maidens (01 - 09) (2003 - 2004)
description:
Batman - Death and the Maidens (01 - 09) (2003 - 2004)


Eisner Award-nominated writer Greg Rucka (GOTHAM CENTRAL, Wolverine) teams up with legendary artist Klaus Janson (BATMAN: THE DARK KNIGHT RETURNS) for a miniseries that pits Batman against one of his greatest foes: Ra's al Ghul! After centuries, time has caught up with al Ghul, and only his greatest enemy can save him! Can these longtime enemies become allies?
